	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1" facs="R 6456-40 (04).jpg"/>
			<p>I have the honor to present a summary of recent <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1068" type="subject"
					>press </term>items relative to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-337" type="subject">anti-Jewish
					measures</term> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html">Rumania</placeName>. <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-585" type="subject">Confiscation of property</term> and <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-556" type="subject">compulsory labor</term> have apparently been the
				principal weapons employed in recent weeks against the <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html"
					>Rumanian</placeName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jewry</term>, although additional forms of taxation
				have also been directed at this <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1062" type="subject">minority</term>.
				[...]</p>
			<pb n="4" facs="R 6456-40 (07).jpg"/>
			<p>In connection with the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-812" type="subject">announcement</term> by the
					<orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-004295">Bulgarian Government</orgName> that all <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> within <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/727011/sofia.html">Sofia</placeName> were to leave the city within a few days, <orgName
					ref="#ehri_dr_pornunca_vremii">PORUNCA VREMII</orgName> of <date when="1943-05-27">May 27</date> suggested, in addition to heavily
				applauding the action of the <term ref="#ehri_dr_nationalities_bulgarians">Bulgarians</term>, that <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">Ghettos</term> be established in every <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1027" type="subject">Axis</term> country, in order to <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-601" type="subject">suppress</term>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1065" type="subject">communist agitation</term>.</p>
		</body>
